{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A classic 24-point game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to use the four arithmetic operations of addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division to combine the randomly given 4 cards (value between 1 and 13). Each number must be used and can only be used once. If the final calculation result equals 24, you can score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The thinking time for each question is limited, and you need to use your brain to solve the problem as soon as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For each question you solve, a little bit of thinking time will be added.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the game progresses, the difficulty will gradually increase.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the beginning, only cards from A to 10 will appear, and later, cards from A to K will appear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Let's see how long you can hold on!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3397170?t=1739692561","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3397170?t=1739692561","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397170/5e1c567b7960235d46f597b6b422d3a14f623d1e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739692561","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3397170/5e1c567b7960235d46f597b6b422d3a14f623d1e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739692561","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A classic 24-point game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to use the four arithmetic operations of addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division to combine the randomly given 4 cards (value between 1 and 13). Each number must be used and can only be used once. If the final calculation result equals 24, you can score!</p><p class=\"bb